1035
01:08:00,610 --> 01:08:02,312
You heard that?

1036
01:08:02,346 --> 01:08:04,314
I'm sorry.

1037
01:08:04,348 --> 01:08:06,450
It doesn't matter.

1038
01:08:06,483 --> 01:08:09,085
I wanted an adventure
