1045
01:08:24,901 --> 01:08:27,437
- I wanted to have some fun.
- So, that's it?

1046
01:08:29,839 --> 01:08:32,108
Just running around naked,
communing with nature?

1047
01:08:32,142 --> 01:08:34,077
I've always been
an optimist.

1048
01:08:34,110 --> 01:08:36,213
I also thought I might
win the big prize.

1049
