like her every day.

1060
01:09:05,442 --> 01:09:07,444
Yep, I see it a lot.

1061
01:09:07,477 --> 01:09:10,247
I can't imagine
being a cop.

1062
01:09:10,280 --> 01:09:12,081
I like it.

1063
01:09:12,115 --> 01:09:14,384
You get to carve out
your little piece of
