I sleep better.

1069
01:09:25,795 --> 01:09:28,365
So, Sam...

1070
01:09:29,366 --> 01:09:31,268
What would you
have spent the money on...

1071
01:09:31,301 --> 01:09:33,703
If you won?

1072
01:09:33,737 --> 01:09:35,772
Hot dogs and beer.

1073
01:09:37,407 --> 01:09:39,476
You think I'm kidding?

1074
01:09:52,055 --> 01:09:53,890
