1079
01:10:04,167 --> 01:10:05,935
That won't be
a problem.

1080
01:10:19,115 --> 01:10:21,351
Think the storm
has passed?

1081
01:10:21,385 --> 01:10:22,586
I don't know.

1082
01:10:22,619 --> 01:10:24,388
I'm just glad
the rain has let up.

1083
01:10:24,421 --> 01:10:27,891
Steve, you've
covered hurricanes,
what do you think?

1084
01:10:27,924 --> 01:10:30,093
No... This is just
the calm

1085
01:10:30,126 --> 01:10:32,095
before it all
hits the fan.

1086
01:10:32,128 --> 01:10:33,930
Little pockets
of easy weather

1087
