What happened?

1096
01:11:29,686 --> 01:11:31,855
What the hell was that?!

1097
01:11:32,922 --> 01:11:35,325
Okay, check it out!
You guys go that way!

1098
01:11:35,359 --> 01:11:37,527
Split up!

1099
